Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:42.02,Typeset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(169,186)}Shirogane thắng
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kết quả hôm nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirogane thắng.
