Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.02,Typeset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,299)}Shinomiya Kaguya
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.02,Typeset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(272,362)}Kashiwagi Nagisa
